<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 3484 Sep 14 19:46 wordbot.srv</span></span></pre>

<p><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;">Copy those we require and delete the rest.</span></p>

<pre><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"># cp spin.p12 spog.p12 wordbot.p12 /var/opt/opsware/crypto/word_uploads</span></span>
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"># rm -rf /tmp/word_uploads</span></span></pre>

